  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arcade Mode</h2><br>Play with your friends or fight against them.<br><br>Team up in Arcade Mode to collect powerups and fight waves of bosses.<br><br>1-4 Players, local-coop (or AI substitutes)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle Mode</h2><br>Fight it out in Battle Mode to be the last one standing. Use stage hazards to your advantage.<br><br>2-4 Players, local-coop (or AI substitutes)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge Mode</h2><br>Looking for a challenge? Try Challenge mode to survive the game's hardest difficulty.<br><br>1 Player<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Penelope Mode</h2><br>Have a younger player 2? Penelope mode brings a casual setting and an emphasis on letter-shaped asteroids.<br><br>1-4 Players, local-coop",
